sync-diff.prompt:
Show me detailed differences between my user settings and this project's settings. Please:

1. Read .claude/sync-manifest.json (project)
2. Read ~/.claude/settings.json (user)
3. For each sync group, show:
   ```diff
   ðŸ“ Changes in {group-name} sync group:

   NEW COMMAND:
   + /{command-name}
   +   Description: {desc}
   +   Script: {script}

   UPDATED COMMAND:
   ~ /{command-name}
   ~   {what-changed}

   REMOVED COMMAND:
   - /{command-name}

   VERSION: v{user-version} â†’ v{project-version}
   AUTHOR: {author}
   DATE: {date}
   ```
4. Highlight breaking changes if any
5. Show files that will be modified
6. Offer: [Apply changes] [Skip]

Refer to .claude/docs/INTERNAL-INSTALL-HELPER.xml for diff format.

